NOTE ON ARTWORK

This MIT license covers the source code. The creature and tamer artwork is
original work carried over from the earlier customizer project. The silhouettes
of the four starter creatures were originally sketched with well-known
franchise creatures in mind; if you intend to distribute this game publicly or
commercially, consider redrawing those designs to be clearly distinct. See
README.md and CREDITS.md for details.
